{"tid":2108995,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「世界不允許北京建海上帝國」 美撐南海仲裁 反華「九段線」主張","createTime":"2020-07-15T02:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T03:21:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"410c47f24b4044554ec0bcb5ea32d16b06d6aabb","tid":2108995,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:29:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200715/ZWWJALA3PCWPBD6XV5II3CQRPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200715%2FZWWJALA3PCWPBD6XV5II3CQRPI%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuJa0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=3176ffb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200715%2FZWWJALA3PCWPBD6XV5II3CQRPI%2F&h=b9f88589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200715/ZWWJALA3PCWPBD6XV5II3CQRPI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「世界不允許北京建海上帝國」<br />\n美撐南海仲裁 反華「九段線」主張<br />\n<br />\n南海仲裁案四周年，特朗普政府再出重招，顛覆過往華府在南海問題立場。美國國務卿蓬佩奧周三發聲明，首次正式反對中國在南海的主權聲索，表明認可2016年南海仲裁案，指控北京對南海大部份海域的主張違法，「世界不會允許北京將南海當成自家海上帝國」。中國外交部批評華府挑撥中國與地區國家關係，惟恐南海不亂及興風作浪。<br />\n<br />\n美國6月向聯合國抗議中國對南海非法的主權聲索後，蓬佩奧正式發聲明反對中國主張。他指中國自2009年提出南海「九段線」主張以來，未提供清楚的法律理據；中國對南<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wsT7yQy7xpa_WRfL_5efXU9uf18=/950x654/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KEWFLAM4LYXBQZC6WY7U4BUH64.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwsT7yQy7xpa_WRfL_5efXU9uf18%3D%2F950x654%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKEWFLAM4LYXBQZC6WY7U4BUH64.gif&h=c030f0b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美表明反對北京南海主張，又頻頻派遣軍艦及戰機巡邏演練。&lt;br /&gt;路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱與東南亞「站在一起」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國際法庭裁「九段線」違法<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，仁愛礁、美濟礁（中國稱擁主權）屬菲律賓的主權範圍，又反對中國在南沙群島12海里以外水域、越南外海萬安灘、大馬外海南康暗沙與北康暗沙、汶萊專屬經濟海<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聲明稱，美國尋求在南海維護和平與穩定，但與盟友的共同利益受前所未有威脅。美國不會容許北京視南海為海上帝國，會與東南亞盟友「站在一起」。美國國務院東亞及太<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華斥挑動是非破壞穩定<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅昨反駁，美國作為域外國家，惟恐南海不亂，千方百計在南海挑動是非，興風作浪；又頻繁派遣先進<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國過往在南海爭議島嶼議題上「不持立場」，但就持續以維護航行自由為名，派遣艦機穿越南海。美雖曾批評中國的主權聲索是非法，但從未如此正式反對北京特定主張。南<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n外長王毅昨與菲律賓外長洛欽舉行視像會談，提到杜特爾特上任後改變前些年一味製造對抗做法，中菲關係回升，中方將繼續透過對話處理海上問題。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/美聯社"},{"pid":"c0c02cc4fa57140783904d93087f0b864ca8b3d0","tid":2108995,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"取消香港關係法<br />\n正式斷交<br />\n<br />\nNext step 南海戰爭"},{"pid":"e6253ac0fc9aeb11a84ba54ab9ff061c320e9f3f","tid":2108995,"uid":62714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"劃界劃到入人地門口真係好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0465e886619250bde1de7f687c593ba8bc845e71","tid":2108995,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6253ac0fc9aeb11a84ba54ab9ff061c320e9f3f","tid":2108995,"uid":62714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"劃界劃到入人地門口真係好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:32:59.000Z","msg":"中華民國個11段線仲誇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448e6f504648bd629e4dae58dd94b2aa6e0ff658","tid":2108995,"uid":21225,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ahspwa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ahspwa.jpg&h=9efa387f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海上帝國"},{"pid":"5043d14884aa0b7db64e8ca08c34a7c2b809af5e","tid":2108995,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0